Construct query entity(type(FigureSkater),careerStation(Skateboarding),birthPlace(Sweden)) 
SELECT *
WHERE { ?subject <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/FigureSkater> ;

Construct query entity(type(Person),otherOccupation(Skateboarding),birthPlace(Sweden)) 
SELECT *
WHERE { ?subject <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Person> ; 
<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/otherOccupation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding> ; 
<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden> . }

The query did not return any data. 

Construct query entity(type,otherOccupation(Skateboarding),birthPlace(Sweden)) 
SELECT *
WHERE { ?subject <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> ?type ;

Construct query entity(type(SoccerPlayer),careerStation(Skateboarding),birthPlace(Sweden)) 
SELECT *
WHERE { ?subject <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/SoccerPlayer> ; 
<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/careerStation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding> ; 
<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden> . }

The query did not return any data. 

Construct query entity(type,careerStation(Skateboarding),birthPlace(Sweden)) 
SELECT *
WHERE { ?subject <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> ?type ; 
<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/careerStation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding> ; 
<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden> . }

Construct query entity(type(SoccerPlayer),careerStation,birthPlace(Sweden)) 
SELECT *

SELECT *
WHERE { ?subject <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/VoiceActor> ; 
<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/careerStation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding> ; 
<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden> . }

The query did not return any data.
